-news/stardew-valley-launches-absolutely-massive-1-6-update-3604021">在 1.6 版本发布后</a>，许多<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/stardew-valley-mods-update-1-6-3603560">游戏中最受欢迎的模组仍然可以使用</a>。还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/stardew-valley-1-6-how-to-get-meowmere-sword-3607518">一把秘密的<em>泰拉瑞亚</em>剑可供玩家解锁</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/stardew-valley-fans-have-a-new-queer-anthem-3619434">《星露谷物语》粉丝们有一首新的酷儿赞歌</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
